# Volunteer Profile Ontology – Causes and Requirements / Equipment & Resources
# Aligned with Volunteering Data Model and volunteer-profile-manager
# https://github.com/theodi/volunteer-profile-manager/blob/main/src/ontology/volunteer.ttl
